job_lists.content:
Job Responsibilities:
• Design and develop interactive web applications that enable customers to navigate, uncover valuable insight and tell stories from billions of content items across print, social and broadcast media; 
• Develop reusable front-end components using advance technology like HTML5, LESS, React, Flex, Node.JS and Flexible, serving thousands of corporate customers in the Asia region; 
• Be an integral part of product/engineering group to define, design and build WOW products; 
• Work closely with UX team to ensure technical achievability and accurate implementation of design front-end design solutions; 
• Translate designs and style guides provided by the UX team into functional, stable and high performance user interfaces; 
• Contribute to continuous improvement on user interface, software architecture or new technologies; 
• Stay in current and new web technology trends and front-end developments;

job_lists.other_condition:
Job Requirements:
• Bachelor degree holder or above in Computer Science or related discipline;
• Strong experience in front-end development using JavaScript frameworks and libraries, including but not limited to React.JS, Angular.JS, Backbone.JS, Meteor.JS, jQuery Bootstrap;
• Hands-on experience in implementing responsive web applications;
• Advantage on experience in developing reusable UI components; Advantage on knowledge in Node.js;
• Well versed in software engineering principles, frameworks, patterns and tools;
• Attention to detail with sensitive UI and user-system interaction. Good analytical and problem solving skills;
• Self-directed team player who thrives in a continually changing environment.
• Passionate on writing clean, semantic and industrial graded code; Curious on various industrial standard frameworks;
• Fresh graduate will be considered.
• 電腦相關專業本科及以上學歷 , 2年以上前端開發經驗； 
• 優秀的分析問題、解決問題和快速學習能力，對解決具有挑戰性的問題充滿激情； 
• 對編碼有激情，熱衷開發簡潔、高效、易維護的程式，符合行業標準； 
• 熟練掌握 Javascript,CSS,HTML,HTML5語言程式設計； 
• 熟悉 HTTP通信協定 , 掌握 RESTFUL 或 SOAP Web 服務協定； 
• 熟悉和掌握至少一種原始程式碼管理軟體（ SVN/CVS/GIT）； 
• 有 Node.JS開發經驗，理解 Node.JS非同步非阻塞的程式設計模型者優先； 
• 有多屏 Web專案開發或海量資料視覺化經驗者優先； 
• 優秀應屆畢業生也可考慮。

job_lists.content:
Job Responsibilities:
• Design and develop interactive web applications that enable customers to navigate, uncover valuable insight and tell stories from billions of content items across print, social and broadcast media; 
• Develop high performance business logic layer for rapid data retrieval and complex business operations, serving thousands of corporate customers in the Asia region; 
• Be an integral part of product/engineering group to define, design and build WOW products; 
• Work closely with Backend data team to ensure technical achievability and deliver timely Market Intelligent and Business Intelligent solutions;
• Contribute to continuous improvement on application performance and deploy effective caching mechanism; 
• Stay in current and new web technology trends and backend technology. 

職位描述：
• 設計和開發符合客戶需求的網頁交互應用程式，使客戶能從數億條紙媒、網路社交媒體和廣播媒體中提取有價值資訊； 
• 研發高性能業務處理技術，來滿足快速大量的資料增長及複雜的業務邏輯，服務於數千家亞洲區客戶； 
• 團隊精神，具有產品思維，從產品角度定義、設計、開發出叫好又叫座的產品；
• 密切與後端資料團隊合作，保證技術的可實現性和提供及時的市場、商業智慧解決方案； 
• 有性能優化和緩存部署經驗； 
• 關注前沿技術發展趨勢，學習最新後端框架。

job_lists.other_condition:
Job Requirements:
• Bachelor degree holder or above in Computer Science or related discipline;
• Strong experience in Java, J2EE, SSH;
• Familiar with at least one source code management software (SVN/CVS/GIT);
• Hands-on experience in continuous improvement on application performance and deploy effective caching mechanism;
• Advantage on experience in using MySQL/Oracle/Mongo DB, and other NoSQL;
• Well versed in software engineering principles, frameworks, patterns and tools;
• Good analytical and problem solving skills;
• Self-directed team player who thrives in a continually changing environment.
• Passionate on writing clean, semantic and industrial graded code; Curious on various industrial standard frameworks;

職位要求： 
• 電腦相關專業本科及以上學歷，本科3年以上工作經驗，碩士1年以上工作經驗； 
• 優秀的分析問題、解決問題和快速學習能力，對解決具有挑戰性的問題充滿激情； 
• 對編碼有激情，熱衷開發簡潔、高效、易維護的程式，符合行業標準； 
• 精通 JAVA開發,對 GC、多執行緒,同步機制有深入瞭解 , 熟練掌握 Eclipse 等開發工具； 
• 熟悉 J2EE主流框架及相關開發， spring、 hibernate、 struts2等； 
• 熟悉 HTTP通信協定 , 掌握 RESTFUL or SOAP Web 服務協定； 
• 熟悉和掌握至少一種原始程式碼管理軟體（ SVN/CVS/GIT）； 
• 熟練使用 Mysql/Oracle/MongoDB 等關係及非關係型數據庫產品；
• 熟悉Lucene 等開源搜索框架及爬蟲技術優先；
• 善於溝通表達，具備良好的團隊協作能力；性格樂觀開朗，富於激情和創造力。
